des:
Online, on your smart device and on DAB, we play all the legends from Bowie to Madonna, Spice Girls to Take That, and all the greatest hits are on Wigan One.

National and local news for Wigan on the hour, weather, sport and what’s on. Greatest hits by the biggest artists on your Wigan One.
